/**
 * CompatibleStacks.astro
 *
 * Railway-style minimal logo grid. Every logo here is a verified
 * official SVG from Simple Icons (CC0). No wordmark placeholders,
 * no invented marks — if a brand doesn't have a real SVG, it
 * doesn't ship.
 *
 * Mixed verticals (AI infra + payments + cloud + data) signals
 * AEGIS plugs into the stacks teams already run. Two rows of
 * eight = sixteen logos, intentionally heterogeneous so a visitor
 * lands on something they recognize.
 */

